Apply Householder transformations and the row permutation P to y.

Parameters:
a sparse matrix containing the vectors defining the Householder transformations
beta scaling factors for the Householder transformations
y contents of a V->m by nrhs dense matrix
p 0-based permutation vector of length V->m
nrhs number of right hand sides (i.e. ncol(y))
trans logical value - if TRUE create Q'y[p] otherwise Qy[p]
